  "title": "Junior Sales Ambassador // 1-1 coaching provided",
  "description": "<p>🤔From your perspective, what’s more valuable in the workforce — formal qualifications📚 or personal skills🧠?</p>\n<p>If you say PERSONAL SKILLS, why not onboard on this adventurous and rewarding career? ✨</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>We will explore these SKILLS:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Communication</li>\n  <li>Problem Solving</li>\n  <li>Relationship Building</li>\n  <li>Negotiation</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you think you have these skills, then you are definitely at an ADVANTAGE!</p>\n<p>If no, no worries because we provided ALL the resources you need, like 1-TO-1 MENTORSHIP!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Assist In:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop and execute marketing campaigns</li>\n  <li>Represent client’s brand with energy and professionalism</li>\n  <li>Promote client’s products/services with confidence</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with supportive teammates and leadership who are invested in your success</li>\n  <li>Track progress and celebrate your wins!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Get:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>WORK HARD, PLAY HARD environment</li>\n  <li>1-to-1 mentorship</li>\n  <li>A clear career path with advancements from within</li>\n  <li>Supportive team culture that values your growth</li>\n  <li>A chance to reinvent yourself in a future-forward role</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Trust yourself, Trust the process and you will get the RESULTS you want if you put in the EFFORT 🤩</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>APPLY NOW</strong> to embark on this exciting journey with us!</p>",
